The claim with the title 'PoliGraph: NRCC distorts Nolan’s terrorism record ' says In its latest ad, the National Republican Congressional Committee is seeking to make 8th Congressional district rep. Rick Nolan look soft on terrorism. A new spot running this week weaves images Nolan with videos of terrorists, tanks and explosions. “ we all know the growing threat we face today, ” the ad says. “ what we doN’t know is why congressman Rick Nolan voted to release terrorists held at Guantanamo Bay and then voted against funding for our troops fighting the war on terror. ”
